description:
This 65 minute, high definition training is a one-stop-shop guide to getting your better job. Topics include;

  • Results Oriented Resumes
  • Video Resumes
  • Cover Letters
  • References
  • Research
  • Networking
  • LinkedIn Training
  • 30-60-90 Day Plan of Action
  • Goal Setting
  • Interview Portfolios
  • Impression Management
  • Story Telling
  • Commonly Asked Questions with Role Play
  • Questions to Ask
  • Compensation Negotiation
  • Follow Up
title: Interview, Resume, & Networking Workshop
